Documentation for Warmup Assignment 2
=====================================

+-------+
| BUILD |
+-------+
	The source code files (.c) as well as the include files (.h) are present in warmup2 directory.
	1) To build the executable 'warmup2'  :  Type "make" or "make warmup2".
	2) To clean the object and temp files :  Type "make clean"

+------+
| SKIP |
+------+

	1) Do not test the following
		./warmup2 -t /etc
                    (where input file /etc is a directory)

