Dropped tokens test 						: working perfectly
Cannot handle <Cntrl+C> at all (ignored or no statistics) 	: Handles < cntrl+c > perfectly
Can handle <Cntrl+C> but statistics way off 			: Handles < cntrl+c > perfectly and statistics are also printed
Not using condition variables and do some kind of busy-wait 	: Only Condition variables used
Synchronization check 						: No semaphores used. Only mutex used
